description:
This is a 11 minute workout called '10 Min HIIT Cycle Bike Workout' from the channel Sunny Health & Fitness.
The workout falls under Cardio/Indoor biking and Cardio/HIIT.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Beginner fitness levels.
You'll need Exercise Bike for this workout.
The workout has a The Firestarter and The Warrior Workout vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Moderate and Challenging.

Original workout description: 10 Min HIIT Cycle Bike Workout

Trying to squeeze a workout into your busy day? This quick 10-minute cycle bike HIIT is a great way to make the most of your time. Follow along with Sunny Trainer Sydney as you push your body to the limit all in just 10 minutes. 

Warm-up 
1 min Progressive 

Workout 
12x 30 sec on (high resistance, all out cadence); 15 sec off (easy recovery)

END WORKOUT
